{"tid":1744691,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"演出業協會提出暫時將演唱會公開發售門票比例上限 由最少3成改為1成","createTime":"2019-11-22T01:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T01:51:39.000Z","uid":3290,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c24d20db4218f5e0488255e8a23ec6b71b9b736a","tid":1744691,"uid":3290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:05:08.000Z","msg":"（2）為業界增加經營彈性，調整銷售門票比例：由於市況不明朗，建議政府為主辦機構提供更大營運彈性，例如<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暫時將公開發售門票比例上限由最少3成改為1成</span></span></strong>，讓演出業可以爭取更多贊助商支持，一方面有助改善經營環境， 另一方面更可幫助贊助商推廣其品牌。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191121/60294121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191121%2F60294121&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt8xPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=acaffd9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191121%2F60294121&h=ee32069c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191121/60294121</a><br />\n<br />\n前提係近排因為反送中條例所以取消咗好多演唱會，所以演出業協會就發聲明提議四點改善措施（詳情可以睇報導，唔貼哂出黎啦）<br />\n其中一點，最令大家關注嘅就係將公開發售門票，由原本嘅三成改為一成<br />\n令原本已經好黑嘅黑洞座位表變成全黑咁濟<br />\n逼大家去幫襯個班贊助商去換演唱會飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58518a8569b498ae627d3571c2ce444d33f00bfa","tid":1744691,"uid":18265,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:07:04.000Z","msg":"一成食自己啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724fc0c5bce2d524898eeb6e3751f4b64fa9ca3e","tid":1744691,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:09:34.000Z","msg":"黃牛價賣票，再原價退票"},{"pid":"b7e058de6581d3b5091689346dfdb03551f3a942","tid":1744691,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:51:08.000Z","msg":"支持！反正我都買唔到，一齊唔好睇，攬炒"},{"pid":"44d40d0cfa65f0e7d2fd0cdea062f1ddb428e202","tid":1744691,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T01:51:39.000Z","msg":"18-11-2019 (原片）香港警察踩示威者頭部<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你好我係拍片嘅本人，有冇人知道個手足點樣？可以幫手retweet 比多啲人睇到,想推到出國際記者報道，謝謝 Twitter link <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Ng18607704/status/119663203131413709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNg18607704%2Fstatus%2F119663203131413709&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt8xPX6nNrjY8iteK6A9FjwF0%3D&h=f69b57fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNg18607704%2Fstatus%2F119663203131413709&h=cadaa24f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Ng18607704/status/119663203131413709</a>"}]}